# Story/Social Relations (tests/evals convenience)
# This file contains relations that are useful in story-style eval suites and toy domains,
# but are not required for the baseline reasoning core.

@ancestorOf:ancestorOf __Relation  # Provide an ancestry relation used in story-style domains.
@:ancestorOf_transitive __TransitiveRelation ancestorOf  # Make ancestry transitively closed for toy reasoning.

@descendantOf:descendantOf __Relation  # Provide a descendant relation used in story-style domains.
